#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create preliminary .cvsignore in the current directory"
msgstr "Ustvari predhodni .cvsignore v trenutnem imeniku"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> is used to create a preliminary "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> in the current directory. It does this based "
"on certain contents it finds in <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> se uporablja za ustvarjanje predhodnega "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> v trenutnem imeniku. To stori na podlagi "
"določene vsebine, ki jo najde v <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No lines will be removed from any existing <filename>.cvsignore</filename>. "
"If there is not already a <filename>.cvsignore</filename> file, it will be "
"added to the cvs repository."
msgstr ""
"Nobena vrstica ne bo odstranjena iz nobene obstoječe <filename>.cvsignore</"
"filename>. Če datoteka <filename>.cvsignore</filename> še ne obstaja, bo "
"dodana v repozitorij cvs."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must have a <filename>Makefile.am</filename> in the current "
"directory for this tool to work."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da morate imeti <filename>Makefile.am</filename> v trenutnem "
"imeniku, da to orodje deluje."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Ta pripomoček je del programa &kde; Software Development Kit. (Komplet za "
"razvoj programske opreme)."
